item.title: Overview of website content
item.description: Here is my post. I finally got it to work. Woo Hoo #Check it out 2+2 ## [1] 4 This website contains my data analysis projects from the computational biology and bioinformatics course taught at UT Austin. The course aims to showcase the power of R for statistics and data sciences. Below you will find the links to my two projects. The first being an exploratory analysis into the impacts of winning a major sports championship on the birth rate of the winning state.
